      <title>随着夏季临近，印度科技中心面临严重缺水</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-17/india-tech-hub-faces-severe-water-shortages-as-summer-approaches</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度的科技中心班加罗尔正因干旱而面临水资源短缺的问题，随着夏季的临近，危机预计将升级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-17/india-tech-hub-faces-severe-water-shortages-as-summer-approaches</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 17 Mar 2024 06:14:07 GMT</pubDate>
